com.blazingdb.calcite.catalog.domain

Class CatalogColumnImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.blazingdb.calcite.catalog.domain.CatalogColumnImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CatalogColumn

    @Entity
public class CatalogColumnImpl
extends Object
implements CatalogColumn

    Representaion of a column in a table

    A CatalogTableImpl contains several columns. The point of this class is to be able to store names and types and persist these via hibernate.
    Author:
    felipe
